The,Buddy,Platform,is,a,service,that,provides,developers,with,cloud,based,solutions,for,their,applications,The,Buddy,Platform,offers,hosted,features,for,applications,such,as,user,accounts,messaging,photo,albums,and,geolocation,services,The,Buddy,Platform,API,allows,developers,to,access,various,functionalities,of,Buddy,Platform,Some,example,API,methods,include,adding,and,editing,user,accounts,adding,friend,lists,accessing,photo,albums,and,implementing,push,notifications,for,their,applications